		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Look for <a href="http://www.two-sdg.demon.co.uk/curbralan/code/dirent/dirent.html" class="postlink">"dirent" by Kevlin Henney</a>. It implements a subset of the <a href="http://opengroup.org/onlinepubs/007908799/xsh/dirent.h.html" class="postlink">POSIX opendir(), readdir(), and closedir()</a> functionality in Windows. I used it in a ROM builder for SMSAdvance.
<br />
<br />Which graphics API are you using? Allegro? SDL? Straight DirectX?

		

